  "body": "- [ YES] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nGet an error when passing the following big number value as uint256\r\n`Error: invalid BigNumber string value (arg=\"value\", value=\"1.267650600228229401496703205376e+30\", version=4.0.28)`\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\nCreate a contract and function within it that accepts uint 256. With truffle test the contract and pass in `(new BigNumber('2')).exponentiatedBy(100)`\r\n\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\nExpect this to work without error\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nGet the error `Error: invalid BigNumber string value (arg=\"value\", value=\"1.267650600228229401496703205376e+30\", version=4.0.28)`\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Mac 10.14.4\r\n* Ethereum client: Ganache CLI v6.4.4 (ganache-core: 2.5.6)\r\nTruffle v5.0.32 (core: 5.0.32)\r\nSolidity - 0.5.10 (solc-js)\r\nNode v10.13.0\r\nWeb3.js v1.2.1\r\n",
